		"name": "news_api",
		"description": "## News API Collection\n\nNews API: [link](https://news-api-assessment.herokuapp.com/api/posts/)\n\nThis is a collection to news api created as test assessment by Dina Iovcheva  [github:broeld/news_api](https://github.com/broeld/news_api)\n\nNews api provides CRUD functions to posts, comments, replies to comments and a few functions to users (create, update and get by id).\n\n#### users\n| endpoint          | description   |\n| ----------------- |:-------------:|\n| POST api/users/   | create user   |\n| GET  api/users/{{user_id}}/     | get user-info (only for your user account) |\n| PUT  api/users/{{user_id}}/     | update user info (only for your user account)|\n\n\n#### posts\n| endpoint          | description   |\n| ----------------- |:-------------:|\n| GET     api/posts/    | get all posts   |\n| POST    api/posts/   | create post (only for users) |\n| GET     api/posts/{{post_id}}/   | get post|\n| PUT     api/posts/{{post_id}}/   | update post (only for author)  |\n| DELETE  api/posts/{{post_id}}/   | delete post (only for author) |\n| POST    api/posts/{{post_id}}/upvote   | upvote/downvote post |\n\n#### comments\n\n| endpoint          | description   |\n| ----------------- |:-------------:|\n| GET     api/posts/{{post_id}}/comments/  | get comments to post   |\n| POST    api/posts/{{post_id}}/comments/  | create comment to post (only for users)  |\n| GET     api/posts/{{post_id}}/comments/{{comment_id}}/   | get comment info |\n| PUT     api/posts/{{post_id}}/comments/{{comment_id}}/   | update comment (only for author) |\n| DELETE  api/posts/{{post_id}}/comments/{{comment_id}}/   | delete comment (only for author) |\n| GET     api/posts/{{post_id}}/comments/{{comment_id}}/replies   | get replies to comment  |\n| POST    api/posts/{{post_id}}/comments/{{comment_id}}/replies   | create reply to comment |",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
	},
